reviews: Works good as a case and looks nice
Case broke within 5 days. Very cheap quality.

I use this mouse for work. I work as a front end web dev. It works really well. I was skeptical at first but I needed a mouse with vertical and horizontal scroll. But it's the best work mouse I've ever had.

The only con is there is no easy way to switch between my computers. I hate that I have to hit the button on the bottom to switch between my pc and mac. Other than that 10/10

review_title: Perfect for any situation (one or two people)
reviews: Use in your home, or out on the trail this pot can do the job!

Love this hat, bought the Black one. Fits good and is higher quality material. Stitching looks great for a hat that I wore all winter and threw in the washing machine a few time. Overall 9/10 very nice

review_title: Decent but not a lot of vanilla.
reviews: I drank 3 of these pods without sugar or cream. On it's own it's decent coffee, however I didnt get too much vanilla.
